{"title":"二叉搜索树以及平衡树","uid":"133e88ef0286fc9536d9eb46e24158ee","slug":"二叉搜索树以及平衡树","date":"2026-02-01T16:00:00.000Z","updated":"2026-02-13T23:01:13.689Z","comments":true,"path":"api/articles/二叉搜索树以及平衡树.json","keywords":null,"cover":null,"content":"<h1 id=\"二叉搜索树\"><a href=\"#二叉搜索树\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"二叉搜索树\"></a>二叉搜索树</h1><p>记录了基本结构，包含插入函数和删除函数。<br>注意，这两个函数的第一个参数一般使用根节点，也即从根节点出发搜索空位&#x2F;指定的值，搜索到就插入&#x2F;删除。</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight cpp\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br><span class=\"line\">24</span><br><span class=\"line\">25</span><br><span class=\"line\">26</span><br><span class=\"line\">27</span><br><span class=\"line\">28</span><br><span class=\"line\">29</span><br><span class=\"line\">30</span><br><span class=\"line\">31</span><br><span class=\"line\">32</span><br><span class=\"line\">33</span><br><span class=\"line\">34</span><br><span class=\"line\">35</span><br><span class=\"line\">36</span><br><span class=\"line\">37</span><br><span class=\"line\">38</span><br><span class=\"line\">39</span><br><span class=\"line\">40</span><br><span class=\"line\">41</span><br><span class=\"line\">42</span><br><span class=\"line\">43</span><br><span class=\"line\">44</span><br><span class=\"line\">45</span><br><span class=\"line\">46</span><br><span class=\"line\">47</span><br><span class=\"line\">48</span><br><span class=\"line\">49</span><br><span class=\"line\">50</span><br><span class=\"line\">51</span><br><span class=\"line\">52</span><br><span class=\"line\">53</span><br><span class=\"line\">54</span><br><span class=\"line\">55</span><br><span class=\"line\">56</span><br><span class=\"line\">57</span><br><span class=\"line\">58</span><br><span class=\"line\">59</span><br><span class=\"line\">60</span><br><span class=\"line\">61</span><br><span class=\"line\">62</span><br><span class=\"line\">63</span><br><span class=\"line\">64</span><br><span class=\"line\">65</span><br><span class=\"line\">66</span><br><span class=\"line\">67</span><br><span class=\"line\">68</span><br><span class=\"line\">69</span><br><span class=\"line\">70</span><br><span class=\"line\">71</span><br><span class=\"line\">72</span><br><span class=\"line\">73</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"meta\">#<span class=\"keyword\">include</span> <span class=\"string\">&lt;iostream&gt;</span></span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">using</span> <span class=\"keyword\">namespace</span> std;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"type\">const</span> <span class=\"type\">int</span> N = <span class=\"number\">100010</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">struct</span> <span class=\"title class_\">Node</span> &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"type\">int</span> val;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"type\">int</span> l, r; <span class=\"comment\">// l和r存储的是数组下标，不是指针</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125; tr[N];</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"type\">int</span> idx = <span class=\"number\">0</span>; <span class=\"comment\">// 这里的 idx 相当于内存分配指针</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"type\">int</span> root = <span class=\"number\">0</span>; <span class=\"comment\">// 0 表示空地址 (NULL)</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// 申请新节点 (类似于 new Node(v))</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"type\">int</span> <span class=\"title\">new_node</span><span class=\"params\">(<span class=\"type\">int</span> v)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    idx++;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    tr[idx].val = v;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    tr[idx].l = <span class=\"number\">0</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    tr[idx].r = <span class=\"number\">0</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> idx;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// 插入操作</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// u 是引用，代表当前节点在父节点中的“钩子”</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"type\">void</span> <span class=\"title\">insert</span><span class=\"params\">(<span class=\"type\">int</span> &amp;u, <span class=\"type\">int</span> v)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">if</span> (u == <span class=\"number\">0</span>) &#123; <span class=\"comment\">// 如果当前位置是空的，直接把新节点挂在这里</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        u = <span class=\"built_in\">new_node</span>(v);</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">return</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">if</span> (v &lt; tr[u].val) <span class=\"built_in\">insert</span>(tr[u].l, v);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">else</span> <span class=\"keyword\">if</span> (v &gt; tr[u].val) <span class=\"built_in\">insert</span>(tr[u].r, v);</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// 辅助函数：找子树中最小值的节点下标</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"type\">int</span> <span class=\"title\">find_min</span><span class=\"params\">(<span class=\"type\">int</span> u)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">while</span> (tr[u].l != <span class=\"number\">0</span>) u = tr[u].l;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> u;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// 类似也有find_max，只要把while里面的tr[u].l改成tr[u].r即可</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// 删除操作</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"type\">void</span> <span class=\"title\">remove</span><span class=\"params\">(<span class=\"type\">int</span> &amp;u, <span class=\"type\">int</span> v)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">if</span> (u == <span class=\"number\">0</span>) <span class=\"keyword\">return</span>; <span class=\"comment\">// 没找到</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">if</span> (v &lt; tr[u].val) &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"built_in\">remove</span>(tr[u].l, v);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125; </span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">else</span> <span class=\"keyword\">if</span> (v &gt; tr[u].val) &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"built_in\">remove</span>(tr[u].r, v);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125; </span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">else</span> &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"comment\">// 找到了，开始删除</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"comment\">// 情况 A &amp; B: 单子节点或无子节点</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">if</span> (tr[u].l == <span class=\"number\">0</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            u = tr[u].r; <span class=\"comment\">// 用右孩子顶替当前位置 (如果是0也就是变成空)</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        &#125; </span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">else</span> <span class=\"keyword\">if</span> (tr[u].r == <span class=\"number\">0</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            u = tr[u].l; <span class=\"comment\">// 用左孩子顶替</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        &#125; </span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">else</span> &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"comment\">// 情况 C: 左右都有</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"comment\">// 找右子树的最小值（后继）</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"type\">int</span> successor = <span class=\"built_in\">find_min</span>(tr[u].r);</span><br><span class=\"line\">            </span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"comment\">// 用后继的值覆盖当前节点</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">            tr[u].val = tr[successor].val;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            </span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"comment\">// 递归删除那个后继节点</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"built_in\">remove</span>(tr[u].r, tr[successor].val);</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<h2 id=\"一些细节\"><a href=\"#一些细节\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"一些细节\"></a>一些细节</h2><p>使用引用传递参数的原因：将指针传到下一层。这里是一个不使用引用传递参数的版本，借以理解。</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight cpp\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"type\">int</span> <span class=\"title\">insert</span><span class=\"params\">(<span class=\"type\">int</span> u, <span class=\"type\">int</span> v)</span> </span>&#123; </span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">if</span> (u == <span class=\"number\">0</span>) <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> <span class=\"built_in\">new_node</span>(v); </span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">if</span> (v &lt; tr[u].val) tr[u].l = <span class=\"built_in\">insert</span>(tr[u].l, v);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">else</span> tr[u].r = <span class=\"built_in\">insert</span>(tr[u].r, v); </span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> u; <span class=\"comment\">// 返回当前节点，保持链条不断</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<p>对于删除函数的第三种情况，也即要删除的节点左右均有节点，可以取右子树的最小值或者是左子树的最大值。由二叉搜索树的性质知它们一定是叶子。<br>然后，使用它们的值代替该节点的值，节点索引不变，同时删除原节点（因为是叶子，递归的时候会进入if的第二个分支）。</p>\n<h1 id=\"平衡树\"><a href=\"#平衡树\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"平衡树\"></a>平衡树</h1><p>对于平衡树，最重要的是给节点加入了一个成员h，衡量其高度。这个高度是max(左子树高度，右子树高度)</p>\n<figure class=\"highlight cpp\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br><span class=\"line\">8</span><br><span class=\"line\">9</span><br><span class=\"line\">10</span><br><span class=\"line\">11</span><br><span class=\"line\">12</span><br><span class=\"line\">13</span><br><span class=\"line\">14</span><br><span class=\"line\">15</span><br><span class=\"line\">16</span><br><span class=\"line\">17</span><br><span class=\"line\">18</span><br><span class=\"line\">19</span><br><span class=\"line\">20</span><br><span class=\"line\">21</span><br><span class=\"line\">22</span><br><span class=\"line\">23</span><br><span class=\"line\">24</span><br><span class=\"line\">25</span><br><span class=\"line\">26</span><br><span class=\"line\">27</span><br><span class=\"line\">28</span><br><span class=\"line\">29</span><br><span class=\"line\">30</span><br><span class=\"line\">31</span><br><span class=\"line\">32</span><br><span class=\"line\">33</span><br><span class=\"line\">34</span><br><span class=\"line\">35</span><br><span class=\"line\">36</span><br><span class=\"line\">37</span><br><span class=\"line\">38</span><br><span class=\"line\">39</span><br><span class=\"line\">40</span><br><span class=\"line\">41</span><br><span class=\"line\">42</span><br><span class=\"line\">43</span><br><span class=\"line\">44</span><br><span class=\"line\">45</span><br><span class=\"line\">46</span><br><span class=\"line\">47</span><br><span class=\"line\">48</span><br><span class=\"line\">49</span><br><span class=\"line\">50</span><br><span class=\"line\">51</span><br><span class=\"line\">52</span><br><span class=\"line\">53</span><br><span class=\"line\">54</span><br><span class=\"line\">55</span><br><span class=\"line\">56</span><br><span class=\"line\">57</span><br><span class=\"line\">58</span><br><span class=\"line\">59</span><br><span class=\"line\">60</span><br><span class=\"line\">61</span><br><span class=\"line\">62</span><br><span class=\"line\">63</span><br><span class=\"line\">64</span><br><span class=\"line\">65</span><br><span class=\"line\">66</span><br><span class=\"line\">67</span><br><span class=\"line\">68</span><br><span class=\"line\">69</span><br><span class=\"line\">70</span><br><span class=\"line\">71</span><br><span class=\"line\">72</span><br><span class=\"line\">73</span><br><span class=\"line\">74</span><br><span class=\"line\">75</span><br><span class=\"line\">76</span><br><span class=\"line\">77</span><br><span class=\"line\">78</span><br><span class=\"line\">79</span><br><span class=\"line\">80</span><br><span class=\"line\">81</span><br><span class=\"line\">82</span><br><span class=\"line\">83</span><br><span class=\"line\">84</span><br><span class=\"line\">85</span><br><span class=\"line\">86</span><br><span class=\"line\">87</span><br><span class=\"line\">88</span><br><span class=\"line\">89</span><br><span class=\"line\">90</span><br><span class=\"line\">91</span><br><span class=\"line\">92</span><br><span class=\"line\">93</span><br><span class=\"line\">94</span><br><span class=\"line\">95</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"keyword\">struct</span> <span class=\"title class_\">Node</span> &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"type\">int</span> val;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"type\">int</span> l, r;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"type\">int</span> h; <span class=\"comment\">// 存高度</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125; tr[N];</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"type\">int</span> idx = <span class=\"number\">0</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"type\">int</span> root = <span class=\"number\">0</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// 更新节点高度</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"type\">void</span> <span class=\"title\">pushup</span><span class=\"params\">(<span class=\"type\">int</span> u)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    tr[u].h = <span class=\"built_in\">max</span>(tr[tr[u].l].h, tr[tr[u].r].h) + <span class=\"number\">1</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// 获取平衡因子 (Balance Factor)</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"type\">int</span> <span class=\"title\">get_balance</span><span class=\"params\">(<span class=\"type\">int</span> u)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> tr[tr[u].l].h - tr[tr[u].r].h;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// 创建新节点</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"type\">int</span> <span class=\"title\">new_node</span><span class=\"params\">(<span class=\"type\">int</span> v)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    idx++;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    tr[idx].val = v;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    tr[idx].l = <span class=\"number\">0</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    tr[idx].r = <span class=\"number\">0</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    tr[idx].h = <span class=\"number\">1</span>; <span class=\"comment\">// 新节点高度为1</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> idx;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// 核心：右旋</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// 注意：这里引用传参 u，直接修改父节点的指向</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"type\">void</span> <span class=\"title\">rotate_right</span><span class=\"params\">(<span class=\"type\">int</span> &amp;u)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"type\">int</span> p = tr[u].l;  <span class=\"comment\">// p 是 u 的左孩子</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    tr[u].l = tr[p].r; <span class=\"comment\">// u 的左边接管 p 的右边</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    tr[p].r = u;      <span class=\"comment\">// p 的右边变成 u</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    </span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"comment\">// 必须先更新子节点 u 的高度，再更新父节点 p 的高度</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"built_in\">pushup</span>(u);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"built_in\">pushup</span>(p);</span><br><span class=\"line\">     </span><br><span class=\"line\">    u = p; <span class=\"comment\">// 将当前位置的根更新为 p</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// 核心：左旋</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"type\">void</span> <span class=\"title\">rotate_left</span><span class=\"params\">(<span class=\"type\">int</span> &amp;u)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"type\">int</span> p = tr[u].r;  <span class=\"comment\">// p 是 u 的右孩子</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    tr[u].r = tr[p].l;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    tr[p].l = u;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    </span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"built_in\">pushup</span>(u);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"built_in\">pushup</span>(p);</span><br><span class=\"line\">    </span><br><span class=\"line\">    u = p;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// 插入操作 (带自动平衡)</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"type\">void</span> <span class=\"title\">insert</span><span class=\"params\">(<span class=\"type\">int</span> &amp;u, <span class=\"type\">int</span> v)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">if</span> (u == <span class=\"number\">0</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        u = <span class=\"built_in\">new_node</span>(v);</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">return</span>;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">if</span> (v &lt; tr[u].val) &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"built_in\">insert</span>(tr[u].l, v);</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"comment\">// 回溯时检查左边是否太高 (平衡因子 == 2)</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">if</span> (<span class=\"built_in\">get_balance</span>(u) == <span class=\"number\">2</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"comment\">// 判断是 LL 还是 LR</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"keyword\">if</span> (<span class=\"built_in\">get_balance</span>(tr[u].l) == <span class=\"number\">1</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                <span class=\"comment\">// LL型: 直接右旋</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">                <span class=\"built_in\">rotate_right</span>(u);</span><br><span class=\"line\">            &#125; <span class=\"keyword\">else</span> &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                <span class=\"comment\">// LR型: 先左旋左孩子，再右旋自己</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">                <span class=\"built_in\">rotate_left</span>(tr[u].l);</span><br><span class=\"line\">                <span class=\"built_in\">rotate_right</span>(u);</span><br><span class=\"line\">            &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125; </span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"keyword\">else</span> <span class=\"keyword\">if</span> (v &gt; tr[u].val) &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"built_in\">insert</span>(tr[u].r, v);</span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"comment\">// 回溯时检查右边是否太高 (平衡因子 == -2)</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">        <span class=\"keyword\">if</span> (<span class=\"built_in\">get_balance</span>(u) == <span class=\"number\">-2</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"comment\">// 判断是 RR 还是 RL</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">            <span class=\"keyword\">if</span> (<span class=\"built_in\">get_balance</span>(tr[u].r) == <span class=\"number\">-1</span>) &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                <span class=\"comment\">// RR型: 直接左旋</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">                <span class=\"built_in\">rotate_left</span>(u);</span><br><span class=\"line\">            &#125; <span class=\"keyword\">else</span> &#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">                <span class=\"comment\">// RL型: 先右旋右孩子，再左旋自己</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">                <span class=\"built_in\">rotate_right</span>(tr[u].r);</span><br><span class=\"line\">                <span class=\"built_in\">rotate_left</span>(u);</span><br><span class=\"line\">            &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">        &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\">    &#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"comment\">// 每次递归回来都要更新当前节点高度</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">    <span class=\"built_in\">pushup</span>(u);</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n\n<h2 id=\"一些细节-1\"><a href=\"#一些细节-1\" class=\"headerlink\" title=\"一些细节\"></a>一些细节</h2><ol>\n<li><p>使用Pushup函数，在插入和删除节点时候维护节点的高度状态</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>右旋：当左子树太高（重）时，我们需要向右旋转。左旋类似</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>四种失衡情况：<br> LL 型（左左）：在左孩子的左侧插入<br> 手段：对当前节点进行一次右旋。</p>\n<p> RR 型（右右）：在右孩子的右侧插入<br> 手段：对当前节点进行一次左旋。</p>\n<p> LR 型（左右）：在左孩子的右侧插入。<br> 手段：先对左孩子左旋（变成 LL 型），再对当前节点右旋。</p>\n<p> RL 型（右左）：在右孩子的左侧插入。<br> 手段：先对右孩子右旋（变成 RR 型），再对当前节点左旋。</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>右旋：<br> 对于当前的节点u，设其左节点为p，那么，将p旋转到u的位置上，同时，p的左子树不变，右子树变成u，然后，将自己原来的右子树挂到u的左边（由于旋转的缘故，这个位置空了）。</p>\n</li>\n<li><p>引用传参的原因：左旋右旋函数通常是在其他函数里被调用的，如果不引用传参会更加麻烦一点。比如说，</p>\n</li>\n</ol>\n<figure class=\"highlight cpp\"><table><tr><td class=\"gutter\"><pre><span class=\"line\">1</span><br><span class=\"line\">2</span><br><span class=\"line\">3</span><br><span class=\"line\">4</span><br><span class=\"line\">5</span><br><span class=\"line\">6</span><br><span class=\"line\">7</span><br></pre></td><td class=\"code\"><pre><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// 必须有返回值</span></span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"function\"><span class=\"type\">int</span> <span class=\"title\">rotate_right</span><span class=\"params\">(<span class=\"type\">int</span> u)</span> </span>&#123;</span><br><span class=\"line\">   <span class=\"comment\">// ... 旋转逻辑 ...</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">   <span class=\"keyword\">return</span> p;</span><br><span class=\"line\">&#125;</span><br><span class=\"line\"><span class=\"comment\">// 调用的时候必须手动接住！</span></span><br><span class=\"line\">tr[Father].l = <span class=\"built_in\">rotate_right</span>(tr[Father].l);</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>\n<p>当u节点的上级节点Father发现自己的左子节点u失衡了需要旋转的时候，就要传入参数。如果不用引用传递参数的话就多写一句赋值语句。</p>\n","feature":true,"text":"二叉搜索树记录了基本结构，包含插入函数和删除函数。注意，这两个函数的第一个参数一般使用根节点，也即从根节点出发搜索空位/指定的值，搜索到就插入/删除。 1234...","permalink":"/post/二叉搜索树以及平衡树","photos":[],"count_time":{"symbolsCount":"4.9k","symbolsTime":"4 mins."},"categories":[{"name":"算法","slug":"算法","count":15,"path":"api/categories/算法.json"},{"name":"模板","slug":"算法/模板","count":9,"path":"api/categories/算法/模板.json"}],"tags":[{"name":"平衡树","slug":"平衡树","count":1,"path":"api/tags/平衡树.json"}],"toc":"<ol class=\"toc\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E4%BA%8C%E5%8F%89%E6%90%9C%E7%B4%A2%E6%A0%91\"><span class=\"toc-text\">二叉搜索树</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E4%B8%80%E4%BA%9B%E7%BB%86%E8%8A%82\"><span class=\"toc-text\">一些细节</span></a></li></ol></li><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-1\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E5%B9%B3%E8%A1%A1%E6%A0%91\"><span class=\"toc-text\">平衡树</span></a><ol class=\"toc-child\"><li class=\"toc-item toc-level-2\"><a class=\"toc-link\" href=\"#%E4%B8%80%E4%BA%9B%E7%BB%86%E8%8A%82-1\"><span class=\"toc-text\">一些细节</span></a></li></ol></li></ol>","author":{"name":"LHY","slug":"blog-author","avatar":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/256316666?s=400&u=531212165de7b7b90dc6ec2dd44404fc88f4a435&v=4","link":"/","description":"天空中的宝石应该交由天空去寻找","socials":{"github":"","twitter":"","stackoverflow":"","we